STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Claudio J. MARQUEZ-GUZMAN, Defendant-Petitioner. C-445 September Term 2017
079707 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 13, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000820-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
